Rating: 4
This is delicious, but is inclined to burn when cooked in butter. This may be because the sugary OJ burns, as does the butter. Better to use a combination of cooking oil and butter, or just cooking oil. I liked this French toast with just a very thin layer of orange marmalade plus the maple syrup. The powdered sugar is absolutely great!

